== DDSX11 Options

The DDSX11 facet provides the following additional flags

[width="100%",cols="<2m,<3m,<4a",options="header",]
|=======================================================================
|Short command line option|
Long command line or sub-option|
Description

| -Gddsx11,idds | |
Generate the IDL file for DDSX11 (_dds.idl)

| -Gddsx11,ite | |
Generate the IDL file for a DDSX11 typed datareader and datawriter

| -Gddsx11,its | |
Generate the implementation files for the DDSX11 type support

|-Gddsx11,adds | |
Generate all DDSX11 related files

|-Gddsx11,traits | |
Generate user defined conversion traits for DDSX11

|-Sddsx11,nddslfc | |
Do not generate life cycle traits for DDSX11 NDDS support(generated by default). *DDSX11 core use only.*

|=======================================================================
